I replace the 0 with 1:


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
weight <- ifelse(weight == 0, 1, weight)

table.income <- table.income %>% select(-cumrelfreqInc) %>% 
  mutate(share_decile = weight)

table.income %>% 
  mutate(share_rest = 1 - weight) -> table.income

table.income %>% gt()
```

